    "The modern evolution of AI is characterised by the interplay and development of symbolic AI, machine learning, deep learning and generative AI.",
    "The machine learning period proved that instead of programming rigid rules, scientists began to teach computers to determine rules based on large amounts of data.",
    "Machine learning allowed systems to adapt to new situations and improve their performance over time.",
    "Deep learning has become a key area of machine learning, using multi-layered neural networks (deep neural networks) to automatically identify abstractions and features in data.",
    "This has led to significant advances in pattern recognition, natural language processing and other areas."
